You can work around that using a &quot;Box&quot; type that wraps a value in a reference:<p><pre><code>    class Box<T> {
        var contents : T
        init(_ initialContents : T) {
            contents = initialContents
        }
    }

    enum BinaryTree {
        case Leaf
        case Branch(Box<BinaryTree>, Box<BinaryTree>)
    }</code></pre>
